org.palo.api
Interface VirtualObject

Deprecated. Please do not use!! This class is for internal usage only! 

public interface VirtualObject

A VirtualObject classifies all palo object which are virtual, i.e. their creation based on virtual definitions like VirtualCubeDefinition or VirtualDimensionDefinition.
